Had a little bit of trouble getting the cakes to stay together, so I opted to bake them, and they came out GREAT! Everyone LOVED the chili-mayo, so I ended up making more of it. Made them for Mother's Day lunch, so it was worth it to spend the extra money on real lump crab meat (Mom never skimped on us!)

