The absolute best. I used canned lump crab, $24 p/p and it was fabulous. My guests commented that these were the best they ever had, I agree. My first time making crab cakes too and I'm impreseed. I used all 5 cups of bread crumbs and had held together. I also added a little more oil to cook them. Tasted great the next day, warmed in the oven. Enjoy

